    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. You really won't find one in better condition. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
