    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, scratches, or road chips, having been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating since day one. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and every electronic feature\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open-checkbook policy, documented by a complete folder of service records from the authorized dealership. The engine bay is spotless, the undercarriage is free of debris, and the tires are a matching set of high-performance rubber with nearly full tread remaining. This is a smoke-free, pet-free, and accident-free example that will satisfy even the most discerning enthusiast. For the buyer who demands perfection without compromise, this is the finest example currently available on the market.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
