      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. I have absolutely babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s still in total showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like an absolute dream. I'm looking for a great new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
